(161, 'ConditionUtilisation', '<u>Terms of use :</u><br/><br/>\r\n\r\nGeneral Conditions for use and sellings on line on the Web Site www.junive.com/alex/Euromedecine (Hôtel du Parc Euromédecine in Montpellier-Grabels) <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>1. Description of the services : </u><br/>\r\nThis Web Site (www.junive.com/alex/Euromedecine) was created and managed by the SARL M.G.I. (Hôtel du Parc Euromédecine in Montpellier-Grabels).The site gives the users the opportunity of making reservations, on line, of rooms in our hotel. <br/><br/>\r\n<u>2. Confidentiality of the information : </u><br/>\r\nwww.junive.com/alex/Euromedecine (sarl M.G.I.) commits itself to respect your privacy. There is no way we give your personal information to a third party. The information provided when you make a reservation only aims at ensuring you''ll benefit from a professionnal service.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u> 3. Guarantee with credit card : </u><br/>\r\nYou cannot make a reservation if you don''t own a credit card ! <br/><br/>\r\nwww.junive.com/alex/Euromedecine (sarl M.G.I.) demands the data of your credit card in order for us to be able to guarantee your reservation.We do not ask you to pay extra charge on your credit card for your stay at your arrival. During your stay at the hotel, you can use whatever form of payment you may like. (See  our page « Our Services »). <br/><br/>\r\nWe get the information appearing on your credit card through a secured server. We use the state-of-the-art technology in terms of security, your credit card number is encoded by the SSL System (Secure Socket Layer); our SSL certificate was provided to us by Thawte. Our server is protected against unauthorised access, which means that we guarantee an unfailing  security system as regards the credit card number that is given to us. <br/><br/>\r\nTherefore, we can assure you that any transaction we make is a 100% secured. If your card is used fraudulently while visiting the Web Site www.junive.com/alex/Euromedecine, the transmitting bank of your credit card will be obliged to pay the amounts debited fraudulently.<br/><br/>\r\nThe references on your credit card will be saved by our server until your arrival at the hotel. After your departure, they will be deleted.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>4. Free Services : </u><br/>\r\nOur service on line is free. We do not add any extra charge on the rate of the room.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>5. Cancellation : </u><br/>\r\nYou might have to cancel your stay. In this case, would you please read attentively and follow the instructions appearing in the e-mail confirmation.<br/><br/>\r\nWould you please consult the conditions for cancellation described in the sixth paragraph bellow.<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>6. Conditions for cancellation : </u><br/>\r\nRoom rentals go from noon to noon. If you tell us your credit card number, your reservation of a room is guaranteed. For a late arrival expected after 11p.m, you have to contact the hotel directly before you arrive. Our phone number is : 0033(0)467524333.<br/><br/>\r\nFor any cancellation, you have to phone to inform the hotel at least before 6 p.m the day you plan to arrive, at this number. A cancellation number will be given to you. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\nFor any reservation not cancelled before 6 p.m the day of your arrival or if you don''t come to the hotel at all (no-show), we''ll be obliged to make you pay the rate of the first night which will be charged on your credit card. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>7. When will you receive an e-mail from us ?</u> <br/>\r\nOnce you''ve made your reservation, you receive an e-mail of confirmation with all the information regarding your reservation.<br/><br/>\r\nThe hotel might ask you a few supplementary details either after your reservation on line or after the comment you have added to it. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<u>8. We decline all responsibilities : </u><br/>\r\nThe Web Site of the Hôtel du Parc Euromédecine in Montpellier-Grabels \r\n(www.junive.com/alex/Euromedecine) (sarl M.G.I.) was created with great caution. Our hotel may modify the information appearing on its Web Site, as well as rates and availabilities at any moment. That''s why we recommend you always check the information provided before doing anything or relying on them. <br/><br/>\r\nFor any suggestion or comment on this declaration, you can send an e-mail to : hotelparceuromedecine@orange.fr,<br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>9. Claims : </u><br/>\r\nThe sarl M.G.I. (Hôtel du Parc Euromédecine in Montpellier-Grabels) in a company registered in France. Any kind of litigation both in the interpretation and in the application of the current conditions of use and selling will be subject to French laws and to the competence of the High Court of Commerce in Montpellier. <br/><br/>\r\n\r\n<u>10. Translations : </u><br/>\r\nIn order to provide the best service possible to our clients, these Conditions of use are available in two languages. If there are differences between the English version and the French version about these Conditions, only the French version will be valid.\r\n'),
