(9, 3, 'body', '<table style="width: 972px; height: 347px;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="cell_title">The children''s house &laquo;The Sparrow&raquo;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="cell_text" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p><img style="float: left; margin: 2px 5px 0px 2px;" src=" ../image/casa site.jpg " alt="" width="253" height="184" />&nbsp;In 2001, Chantal, Gil and their son Aron arrived&nbsp;in Peru, they become established in Ayacucho, city lodged in the middle of Peruvian Andes. In their luggages a quantity of considerable love, the happiness to be shared&nbsp; and as exemple the model of Mother Theresa from Calcuta. Gil and his wife&nbsp;started the casa on March 5th 2002.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In the eighties and till the end of the nineties, Ayacucho was the city most hit in all Peru by the terrorism of The&nbsp;Shining Path&nbsp;(El Sendero Luminoso) and&nbsp;by the special companies of the army repression.</p>\r\n<p>The actual figures mention of more than 70.000 dead and disappeared throughout clashes. Today the city and his habitants try to forget this hurt past and desire to construct a better future.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Today,&nbsp;The Casa&nbsp;Hogar Los Gorriones&nbsp;accommodate 27 children and work also to assist the peruvian&nbsp;population according to various local activities. Chantale died in March 2008 further to a cancer of the liver, Gil and all his team rally to perpetuate&nbsp;her accomplished job.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table style="float: left; width: 321px; height: 193px;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="cell_title">News of the house</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="cell_text">\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Notice:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We are looking for&nbsp;a volunteer&nbsp;who can 